                        <h3><a href="#">Guideline Status</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>This guideline meets NGC's 2013 (revised) inclusion criteria.</p></div></p>
                        <h3><a href="#">Guideline Availability</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>Available from the <a href="/web/20180713090752/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=50176&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=https%3a%2f%2fwww.brit-thoracic.org.uk%2fstandards-of-care%2fguidelines%2fbtsics-guidelines-for-the-ventilatory-management-of-acute-hypercapnic-respiratory-failure-in-adults%2f" title="British Thoracic Society (BTS) Web site">British Thoracic Society (BTS) Web site</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180713090752im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/>.</p></div></p>
                        <h3><a href="#">Availability of Companion Documents</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>The following are available:</p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc;">
    <li>British Thoracic Society. Web appendix 1: literature search strategy. London (UK): British Thoracic Society; 2016 Mar. 11 p. Available from the <a href="/web/20180713090752/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=50176&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=https%3a%2f%2fwww.brit-thoracic.org.uk%2fdocument-library%2fclinical-information%2facute-hypercapnic-respiratory-failure%2fweb-appendix-1-search-strategy-and-clinical-questions%2f" title="British Thoracic Society (BTS) Web site">British Thoracic Society (BTS) Web site</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180713090752im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/>. </li>
    <li>British Thoracic Society. Web appendix 2: evidence tables. London (UK): British Thoracic Society; 2015 Dec 15. 31 p. Available from the <a href="/web/20180713090752/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=50176&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=https%3a%2f%2fwww.brit-thoracic.org.uk%2fdocument-library%2fclinical-information%2facute-hypercapnic-respiratory-failure%2fweb-appendix-2-evidence-tables%2f" title="BTS Web site">BTS Web site</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180713090752im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/>. </li>
    <li>British Thoracic Society. Web appendix 3: slides. London (UK): British Thoracic Society; 2016 Mar 24. 19 p. Available from the <a href="/web/20180713090752/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=50176&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=https%3a%2f%2fwww.brit-thoracic.org.uk%2fdocument-library%2fclinical-information%2facute-hypercapnic-respiratory-failure%2fweb-appendix-3-bts-ics-guideline-slides%2f" title="BTS Web site">BTS Web site</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180713090752im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/>. </li>
    <li>Davidson C, Banham S, Elliott M, Kennedy D, Gelder C, Glossop A, Church C, Creagh-Brown B, Dodd JW, Felton T, Fo&euml;x B, Mansfield L, McDonnell L, Parker R, Patterson CM, Sovani M, Thomas L. British Thoracic Society/Intensive Care Society Guideline for the ventilatory management of acute hypercapnic respiratory failure in adults. Summary of guideline recommendations. BMJ Open Resp Res 2016;3:e000133. Available from the <a href="/web/20180713090752/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=50176&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=http%3a%2f%2fbmjopenrespres.bmj.com%2fcontent%2f3%2f1%2fe000133.full" title="BMJ Open Respiratory Research Web site">BMJ Open Respiratory Research Web site</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180713090752im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/>. </li>
